
Enter REPL:
```sh
nix repl
```

Find package:
```sh
nix-env -qaP [package-name]
```
or, faster:
```sh
nix-env -f '<nixpkgs>' -qaP -A [package-name]
```

Start shell with specific package installed:
```sh
nix-shell -p kubectl kubernetes-helm socat jq
```

System upgrade:
```sh
nixos-rebuild switch --upgrade
```
